{"tid":125591,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"其實雪碧同七喜有咩分別？","createTime":"2017-02-18T15:24:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-20T17:17:41.000Z","uid":62722,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f117951a42fb1e5dbbcc435e1c95ccd7e70351ab","tid":125591,"uid":62722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T15:24:19.000Z","msg":"有冇人分得出？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf1fddb82af5e7e861ee86522a761c4386a0d9b4","tid":125591,"uid":13645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T15:26:01.000Z","msg":"7up 甜d"},{"pid":"bba061b03bad56fe3d8397bb62b9dedfa9277a78","tid":125591,"uid":4363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T15:26:36.000Z","msg":"無記錯包裝同容量好似唔同"},{"pid":"9febe2a2c9a6b4d46fcda4cbb0de67a0a48b92b3","tid":125591,"uid":64349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T15:27:13.000Z","msg":"雪碧爽好多，好氣好多，好強口爆力<br />\n利申飲左六年"},{"pid":"c7338d2fea64a3152ce9f72a07179b0841148e28","tid":125591,"uid":1494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T15:27:19.000Z","msg":"7喜好飲d"},{"pid":"32e3d60f10c52d828a221c61777cc292396561b3","tid":125591,"uid":64349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T15:27:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>雪碧爽好多，<strong>多</strong>氣好多，好強口爆力<br />\n利申飲左六年</blockquote>"},{"pid":"67f458e2bc0d3a0088955b4212992ab6bce95575","tid":125591,"uid":71826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T15:28:00.000Z","msg":"最佳解答<br />\n兩隻汽水雖然味道差不多, 但分別來自不同公司。七喜即是7-up, 是屬於Pepsi (百士可樂) 的, 同一間公司仲有 Pepsi 同 Mirinda (美年達橙汁)。至於雪碧 (Sprite) 是同 Coca Cola (可口可樂) 同一公司, 同公司仲有 Fanta (芬達橙汁)。基本上兩間公司的產品一定是相對的, 你有可樂時我又有可樂, 你有橙汁時我又有橙汁, 佢地係 competitor! <br />\n這個問題和&amp;quot;百事可樂&amp;quot;和&amp;quot;可口可樂&amp;quot;喝起來有什麼不同 <br />\n有異曲同工之妙 <br />\n應該也是看個人的感覺吧~ <br />\n我是覺得雪碧氣泡比較多,比較沒那麼甜 <br />\n七喜氣泡就少一點,但甜度也比較高<br />\nTim &middot; <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">10 年前</span>"},{